{"id":61237,"title":"[Algorithm for examination of bone marrow trephine biopsy specimens in myelodysplastic syndromes].","abstract":"Based on the analysis of more than 1000 bone marrow trephine biopsy specimens from patients with myelodysplastic syndromes before starting any specific therapy, the authors propose histological criteria for their evaluation (an examination algorithm), an optimal panel of immunohistochemical examination, and histological criteria for predicting the course of the disease.","date":"2014-04-21","categories":"Hemic and Lymphatic Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24745194","annotations":[{"name":"Disease","weight":0.804197,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Disease"},{"name":"Histology","weight":0.801553,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Histology"},{"name":"Bone marrow","weight":0.799696,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bone_marrow"},{"name":"Biopsy","weight":0.797552,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Biopsy"},{"name":"Bone","weight":0.72,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bone"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.636795,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Immunohistochemistry","weight":0.268384,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Immunohistochemistry"},{"name":"Syndrome","weight":0.255994,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Syndrome"},{"name":"Algorithm","weight":0.210212,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Algorithm"},{"name":"Test (assessment)","weight":0.18053,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Test_(assessment)"},{"name":"Evaluation","weight":0.0805305,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Evaluation"},{"name":"Myelodysplastic syndrome","weight":0.0636763,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Myelodysplastic_syndrome"},{"name":"Trephine","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Trephine"},{"